E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Last Tap Dance in Springfield: Lisa takes up dancing but discovers that she's not very good at it. Bart and Milhouse duck out of their camping trip and hide out in the mall. (S11 Ep20/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Below Deck
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Real Housewives of Grenada: Chef Anthony takes on his biggest challenge, while the relentless demands of a famous guest push the interior to their limit. (S11 Ep9/17)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Expedition Approximation: Sheldon and Raj try to find out if they could survive a dark-matter research expedition in a salt mine by simulating the conditions in a tunnel. (S8 Ep6) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Thanksgiving Jamboree: Phil spares no expense on a Thanksgiving jamboree. And Hayley has to tell her dad that she'd rather spend the holidays with her boyfriend. (S8 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Alliance: Haley's plan for a fun-filled girls' day with Rainer Shine's teen daughter may be more angst-filled than expected. And Luke finds himself in a compromising position. (S8 Ep8)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Double-Click: Claire can't seem to find the right time to fire an employee, Phil thinks he caught Luke with a girl in his bed, and no one notices that Alex has moved back. (S7 Ep22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: A Stereotypical Day: Jay goes out of his way to make a good impression on the new neighbours. (S8 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Blindsided: The Dunphys and Pritchetts go head-to-head when Luke decides his best chance of getting into college is to run against Manny in the senior class president election. (S8 Ep3)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Gordon revisits three restaurants - Handlebar, Casa Roma and The Black Pearl - to check in with the owners he helped. Has his advice been put to good use? (S3 Ep12) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: Two more singles get wed, but could a bride's pursuit of perfection jeopardise love? Plus: more honeymoon hubbub as one groom threatens the chance of romance. (S10 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: No Loan Again, Naturally: When Homer and Marge's mortgage rate skyrockets, they have to put their house up for sale - and Flanders buys it and becomes their landlord. (S20 Ep12/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Gone Maggie Gone: When Marge is temporarily blinded, Homer loses Maggie to a convent and Lisa has to go undercover as a nun to find her. (S20 Ep13/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Parking Spot Escalation: When non-driver Sheldon finds out that his unused parking space at the university has been reallocated to Howard, he feels undermined. (S6 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Fish Guts Displacement: Sheldon begrudgingly takes care of Amy when she is sick. Bernadette arranges for Howard to go on a fishing trip with her macho father. (S6 Ep10)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Unplugged: Claire and Phil challenge the family to a digital detox contest. (S2 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Halloween: Claire, who loves Halloween, ropes in the whole family to spookify the Dunphy house, but none of it goes quite to plan. (S2 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Cooper Extraction: Sheldon has to go back to Texas when his sister goes into labour. While he's away, the gang gather at the flat to decorate the Christmas tree. (S7 Ep11)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Hesitation Ramification: Penny's big TV acting break hits the cutting-room floor, so Leonard does his best to comfort her, which leads her to ask him a bold question. (S7 Ep12)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Occupation Recalibration: Penny quits her job at the restaurant to pursue her acting career full-time. Bernadette accidentally destroys one of Howard's comics. (S7 Ep13)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Convention Conundrum: After the guys miss out on Comic-Con tickets, Sheldon decides to hold his own comic book convention. The girls take tea at a swanky hotel. (S7 Ep14)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Bank Job: Peralta and Diaz learn there's more to Lt Melanie Hawkins' team than meets the eye as they hunt for the gang of bank robbers. (S4 Ep21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: Crime & Punishment: Peralta and Diaz are framed for a crime they didn't commit. Can their Nine-Nine buddies save them from jail!? (S4 Ep22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Replaceable You: When Homer loses his job to his eager new assistant, he teams up with Ned to reveal her evil past. (S23 Ep4/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Ten-Per-Cent Solution: The TV network cancel Krusty the Clown's show. Can his first agent, Annie (Joan Rivers), help him craft a comeback? (S23 Ep8/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: Two more singles get wed, but could a bride's pursuit of perfection jeopardise love? Plus: more honeymoon hubbub as one groom threatens the chance of romance. (S10 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Rude(ish) Tube Shorts
E4Plus1.uk.description: A short, cheeky clip from Rude Tube's naughty little sister that features a variety of cats doing strange things, some soldiers stuck in the sand and a dog balancing on a rope.

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Misinterpretation Agitation: A smitten doctor turns up at Penny's door after her flirtatious sales techniques for the pharmaceutical company work a little too well. (S8 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Bart vs. Lisa vs. the Third Grade: Bart and Lisa end up in the same class when Bart's held back a year and Lisa is moved up one. (S14 Ep3/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Large Marge: Marge accidentally gets breast implants. (S14 Ep4/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: MAFS UK is back, as a fresh batch of singles marry strangers! Our first couples get wed, but will an unexpected surprise and a potential ick threaten harmony? (S10 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: There's a showstopping entrance and a major wobble as more strangers say 'I do'. And our first newly-weds jet off on their honeymoons, but are cracks forming? (S10 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: More strangers get wed, but will a frosty first impression leave one bride out in the cold? And will there be harmonious honeymoons for our fresh newly-weds? (S10 Ep3)

Film4.uk.title: The Man from Colorado

Film4.uk.title: The Contractor
Film4.uk.description: (2022) Action thriller with Chris Pine. An ex-soldier takes on private work to feed his family, but finds himself in dire straits (danger; not the band). With Kiefer Sutherland.

Film4.uk.title: How to Blow Up a Pipeline
Film4.uk.description: (2022) High-octane eco-thriller. A disparate group of young Americans unite to disrupt the oil industry in an act motivated by everything from the ideological to the downright personal.

Film4.uk.description: (1951) Comedy adventure. Burt Lancaster stars as a Foreign Legion sergeant leading nine men on a dangerous mission to prevent a Berber attack on a North African desert fort.

Film4.uk.title: Payroll
Film4.uk.description: (1961) British crime thriller starring Billie Whitelaw. When Jackie's husband - an armoured van driver - is killed in a heist, she vows to unmask those responsible and take her revenge.

Film4.uk.title: Three Hours to Kill
Film4.uk.description: (1954) Western starring Dana Andrews. A man falsely accused of murder gets a last-minute reprieve from the lynch mob so he can track down the real culprit.

Film4.uk.title: Born Free

Film4.uk.title: Deadpool 2

Film4.uk.title: Carlito's Way

Film4.uk.title: Career Girls
